column2: "<%me>! You came at just the time! Did you see Ane-san?"
"...Great! Looks like she's not here! Echo, if it's here..."
"...Z-Zeno, Zeno! Up, look up!"

"Up...?
U-uwah!"

"Hmm, its power seems alright.
Seems to be in good condition if it didn't break after one use."

"Zieg can do it if he tries!
Don't you think so too, Zeno-boy?"
"A-are you trying to kill us, \u3000Ane-san!"

"It's fine. Labrys' power has decreased as well.
You won't die in just one hit."
"At least deny that killing intent of yours..."
"More importantly, Zeno-boy, you've been pretty cowardly as of late."
"As your teacher, I thought I should say something about this."
"Liar! You just purely wanted to test your new Labrys, didn't you!"
"Oh, don't you understand me well? Then there's no need for me to gloss over things."
"It doesn't feel like there was an attempt to gloss over things, though..."
"You guys sure are a fuss. Just obediently be my match for a trial run of Labrys, already."
"You have Nanaki, don't you. And it's a two-on-one. Not a bad deal at all."
"...E-eh? You're counting me in as well?"
"Oops, can't have you join though. A three-on-one would be too disadvantageous for me, I'd have to run away."
"So the two of us is just enough for you!? Z-Zeno, it doesn't seem like she's joking around!"
"Echo, when Ane-san gets like this, there's no getting through to her. In times like this..."
"In times like this...?"
"As fast as you can, RUN!"

"As fast as you...
H-hey, Zeno! Wait for me!"

"Oh, a game of tag?
This kind of thing, I love it!"
